message: انتهى بي حظي التعيس ان معايا فلوس في حساب PayPal بتاع مصر (عندي واحد تاني في انجلترا). مش عارف اعمل اي حاجة في الفلوس، لا قادر اسحبها علي كارت الفيزا المصري و العمليه بتترفض بدون سبب و لا عارف احولها لحساب PayPal بتاع انجلترا عشان (من الواضح) انك تدفع من رصيدك اللي في باي بال، لازم تدفع من الكريديت كارد! اعمل ايه انا دلوقتي طيب؟

Have you tried linking a UK Card or Payoneer to the Egyptian Paypal account .. and withdraw on it ?

Have you tried DixiPay eWallet? It claims to handle money withdrawal from Egyptian Paypal accounts - I purchased their card, activated and connected it with my EG Paypal and it was successfully connected. Though never was able to send invoices or collect money to my EG Paypal so never had the chance to try the withdrawal to it, but it should work. https://www.facebook.com/DIXIPAY/photos/a.10150238100529347.333652.177045739346/10153242621014347/

A side of the main issue, Unfortunately PayPal and Skrill are not allowed now for GoDaddy payments in few countries including Egypt.  

For the post issue, Does DixiPay is confirmed as above? What  is the exact steps we need to follow to achieve connecting the Paypal, Egyptian Visa and DixiPay? is there a chance to connect to a bank account so we avoid the 4% commission when money returned/withdrawn to a Visa card?

بص من الاخر:
1- Egyptian visa debit cards are not working any more 100% sure
2- Dixipay and such prepaid visa (not issued from Egypt) WILL work
3- You can try to let a third party service widthdraw them for you, check out this website
http://www.traidnt.net/vb/f103/

If you have any visa from outside Egypt, try it. You will lose nothing!
